Additional details

The Globe Electric Smart Track Light is a great start to your smart home automation. Simply install your track light as you would any other, pair it with the GLOBE SUITE App and you're ready to go. Designed and manufactured to perfection, small details were added to create a sleek and dynamic look that adds a modern element to any room while letting you create perfect lighting for any situation. Make sure your track light comes on when you arrive home. Create different moods for different times of the day or simply make sure your light comes on and turns off at the same time every day to conserve energy. Plus, the tunable white feature is great for your health by allowing you to have bright white light in the morning and then a relaxed warm light for evenings. And that's not all. This track light lets you change the color of your room so you can create the perfect mood for any situation. The choice is yours and the options are plentiful. Home automation has never been so easy.

    True mood lighting that I've been looking for for a long time. Took no time at all to install and pair. Some minor cons: -Might just be the Tuya app I use to set the light but I can't set a 24-bit hexadecimal value for the color which is something... See more
    True mood lighting that I've been looking for for a long time. Took no time at all to install and pair.

    Some minor cons:
    -Might just be the Tuya app I use to set the light but I can't set a 24-bit hexadecimal value for the color which is something the app is clearly doing itself.
    -The light desperately wants to pair with your wifi or it'll blink annoyingly for 5 or so min. indicating it's in pair mode when the switch is flipped. Would be nice to have a switch on the device that puts it in a "dumb" mode, but then again, you could always just buy a non-wifi enabled light.
    -Outside cover is really cheap plastic, but frankly no one will notice because the light looks so good.

    I'd give it 4.8 stars, but AMZ wants me to round up.

    4.0 out of 5 starsVerified Purchase
    The Light Works great-- though my wife has a new weapon to troll me with now while I'm working.
    Reviewed in the United States on March 27, 2021
    Color: Brushed Nickel
    So we just installed the light earlier today and we had issues pairing the phone with the light-- we didn't realize that fast blinking= EZ pairing (which is connecting via your home wifi) and slow blinking=AP pairing (which is connecting directly to the lights unique... See more
    So we just installed the light earlier today and we had issues pairing the phone with the light-- we didn't realize that fast blinking= EZ pairing (which is connecting via your home wifi) and slow blinking=AP pairing (which is connecting directly to the lights unique wifi hot spot) My wife figured that out before I did and got the light paired to her phone so now she is controlling the light in my office and using it to troll me from the other room. The videos and the instruction weren't 100% clear on that point and it was a bit of a headache but once we figured that out it worked great and that's the only reason I didn't give 5 stars overall. The light is very bright and it remembers whatever setting you have it on if you manually flip the switch to turn it off as opposed to just using the app - which was another thing I was wondering about that hadn't really been addressed in any of the reviews that I saw. The installation and wiring were incredibly easy even though my house is old and the wiring is terrible. The light has three wires for connection Live, Neutral, and a grounding wire and it comes with everything you need to hook it up. So far I'm very satisfied with the product but if anything goes wrong I'll be sure to update this review.
